{
  "stem": "11067.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I found another hiding place in-- this I thought of, too-- was I put two other necklaces down my hosiery, down my stockings, so that it would land in the instep of my shoes.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so when they turned my suitcases upside down and they searched them, there was nothing there but clothing and the couple of things that my father had given me, such as my personal pictures.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had given me a little alarm clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, that kind of thing, but they found nothing else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we finally reached the border of Holland, and my aunt came on board the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I had to retrieve these things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And somehow, we managed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We then went on to the hook of Holland, and we were there probably around midnight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there we were loaded onto boats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My fond name for them was bathtubs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We single filed off the train, and as randomly as we got off two to a cabin, whoever you happened to be with.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was in a cabin with a six-year-old, and I was eight so I was put in charge.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Some other girls who were 12 and 13 were in a cabin near me and had said to me-- because that was something that was talked about, and I said, I don't have anything for seasickness-- and the girl said, well, if you need something we have Dramamine.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You know, come and get it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Well, once the boat started this little girl was terribly sick, and I wasn't far behind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And when we were ill that way mother used to put a little dab of 4711 cologne on our foreheads.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And this was to make you feel better.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Well, you know, if a little is good, well a lot has to be better.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
